data.value:
Teleopti CCC has encountered a problem and needs to close. We are sorry for the inconvenience. If you were in the middle of something, the information you were working on might be lost.
In order to give us valuable information about this error, we ask you to kindly report it by clicking on the “Send e-mail report” button below. This will open your default e-mail program. Please also include the following:
1. Step by step on how to reproduce the error 2. Information about what data you were working with 3. Screenshot of the error with Teleopti CCC in the background
You can also copy the error message text to the clipboard, and paste it in the e-mail body.
Thank you Teleopti R&D
